  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In relation to the-- to the underground movement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not ask.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just knew that I'm a Jew, whatever I was doing on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they could find out right away by pulling the pants down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this didn't stop them from asking questions about the underground activities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after this period of time, I was transported from [INAUDIBLE] to Pawiak and back from Pawiak to [INAUDIBLE] to Karmelizka Street, to where I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Pawiak, there were a number of people already there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I got--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People that I met, but I never knew them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a difference between a visual contact and actual contact with the people approaching one another.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you were assigned to a-- to a [? camper ?] with other 10 people, and it was an uncomfortable way of sleeping or living or keeping clean.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- only thing that help you was the daily marching outside for a half an hour in the morning and half an hour before, in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, people were beaten up and how-- somehow was dragging my feet, after all these beatings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the only thing I remember there is [INAUDIBLE] to drink the water, I was putting it out on my face and my cut.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not a simple thing, encounter, for simple reason you still did hope that you somehow will live through and be able to think about it in a different manner.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
